$interpreted: Sophie: Still haven't heard from Elio...
Hanbei: I'll bet...that rascal just doesn't like living in our dirty little circus!
Hutchinson: No, I don't think the gentleman Elio is that kind of a person...
Sophie: I...don't think he'd leave without saying good-bye...
Ru-yi: Sophie, don't be upset...
Ru-yi: At today's performance, Ru-yi will ask around. That'll give us some clues!
Sophie: Rune? Where are you so anxious to get to?
Rune: Rune...wants to go...to the harbor.
Sophie: Harbor? Are you meeting someone?
Sophie: Oh great! Then you better get going!
Hutchinson: Yesterday I was at the market buying some things and I saw Rune playing with a child.
Sophie: Looks like Rune is making some friends. What a great start! I guess I can relax a bit!
Hanbei: Sophie, you're not his mom...
Deo: Rune, you're so slow! Making me wait this long!
Rune: Rune...was lost...couldn't find...Master Deo...
Deo: Lost? You blockhead!
Rune: (...Uh-oh...time to...be beaten...)
Unruly Child: I want a Sun Crisp! This time I've got to buy one!
Greedy Child: Giant Turtle! An Owl Cookie! Oooo...Soft Monster Cake!
Angry Child: No pushing! My Cactus Soda is gonna spill!
Jia-shen: No rush here, enough for everybody!
Deo: Rune, help me buy a Soft Monster Cake!
Rune: Is this...an order?
Deo: Yes! It's an order! Go get me one, quickly! Get everything I just asked for!
Deo: Rune, help──!
Deo: Hey, why are you trying to kidnap me?
Rune: Don't...hurt Master Deo.
Hasty Crook: I know you...aren't you the victor from the Colosseum?
Wily Crook: Is it really him?
Wily Crook: Why are you protecting him? Don't you know his father's the head of the slave trade here?
Rune: Slave...trade...?
Hasty Crook: That bastard is evil as can be! Specializes in kidnapping and training slaves! Then he sells the slaves at a high price. He's the worst of the worst!
Hasty Crook: You were a slave, why on earth would you protect him!?
Hasty Crook: You!
Rune: Rune...protects! Don't...come closer!
Hasty Crook: Damn! Thought we could grab the kid and teach him a lesson...didn't think his pops would get such a powerful bodyguard.
Wily Crook: Let's get out of here!
Deo: *sob*...since my dad's a bad guy...*sob*...everybody hates me...no one likes me...
Rune: Master Deo...are you...hurt?
Deo: Rune, I command you to be my friend.
Rune: Rune...will be...your friend.
